search_results.title: Brady Bryson - Biography
search_results.snippet: Brady Bryson is known for Saturday Night Live (1975), Law & Order: Special Victims Unit (1999) and Where to Now? (2020).

search_results.title: Brady O. Bryson (1915-2006), Nuremberg Prosecutor
search_results.snippet: Bryson was the youngest of the U.S. prosecutors who addressed the IMT during the Nuremberg trial. Brady Bryson's path to Nuremberg was typically idiosyncratic.
